#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/05-vi.md:475
msgid "``` $ vi -c \"set nu\" /home/rockstar/file ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/books/admin_guide/05-vi.md:477
msgid ""
"It is also possible to enter the *Ex* commands in a file named `.exrc` put "
"in the user's login directory. At each VI or VIM startup, the commands will "
"be read and applied."
